description:
SEAPORT/FORT POINT: Move right into this stunning studio at The Muse nestled in the vibrant Seaport/Fort Point neighborhood. This newly renovated, sunny unit features high ceilings, exposed brick, original wood beam ceilings, stainless steel appliances, in-unit laundry, a/c, and a common roof deck with amazing city views. Within minutes of your door you can enjoy countless amazing restaurants, night-life options, grocery stores, Trader Joes, gourmet prepared foods shoppe and public transportation. All there is left to do is move in! Experience the perfect blend of historic charm and modern amenities in one of Boston's most dynamic areas!

Rent Fee Includes: Hot Water, Water, Sewerage Disposal, Refuse Removal, Snow Removal, Recreational Facilities, Grounds Maintenance, Laundry Facilities
